    "created_at": "2025-10-17T08:56:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-10-17T08:56:01Z",
    "body": "> May be related to [#4341](https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/4341), with similar workarounds.\n\nyeah, i added jujutsu/jj modules (as linked in https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/6076#issuecomment-3133552083), and both they and the custom git modules to selectively disable/enable them were extremely slow.\nAdding `shell = [\"sh\", \"--norc\"]` lines (as recommended in https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/4341#issuecomment-1236185930) to all the custom modules reduced their runtime from ~500ms-1s to 30ms-60ms",
    "author_association": "NONE",
